strings.Value: "I don't want to get involved in this."
"Go, Linxia! Let's kill this criminal together!"
"Earn some gold, huh? Why not! Let's finish her off, Darven!"
"Oh, you're just in time! To be honest, {d|Darven}I'd{/d} started to worry that you'd be late. Couldn't delay the show any longer."
"So you decided to show up, after all! Just in time – {d|Linxia}I{/d} may require reinforcement!"

"The criminal has summoned the traitor for help. I shouldn't be surprised." {n}{d|Linxia}Linxia's{/d} lips tighten into a thin line.{/n} "Then I'll just have to kill the both of you. Saves me time later."
"Ha! So, you've come all this way just to share with us this valuable piece of information?"
"I've been waiting for this moment for so long!" {n}Darven's smile looks wolfish.{/n}
"Coward! Both of you are cowards and scum! {g|Hellknights}Hellknights{/g}, charge!"
"Oh, really? You've finally been stirred by your duty to act?" {n}Linxia raises her eyebrow in surprise.{/n}

"Ah, a final betrayal at the very end of the story. I would applaud were I not the betrayed party." {n}Darven spits on the ground.{/n} "But you won't take me so easily. Mercenaries, into formation! Time to work for your gold!"

"Ah, a final betrayal at the very end of the story. I would applaud were I not the betrayed party." {n}Darven spits on the ground.{/n} "We had a deal, didn't we, {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}? Well, I'll teach you a lesson about keeping promises. {g|Mammon}Mammon{/g}! I call upon you!"
"Well this is an unlucky twist. Unless..." {n}{d|Darven}Darven{/d} grins,{/n} "… you'd like to earn a little gold instead."
"What is this? Cowardice or betrayal? Clearly I should not have relied on your honesty. {g|Hellknights}Hellknights{/g}, charge!"
"Kill?" {n}Linxia grins.{/n} "Sure. We'll do that. If he's lucky."
"I am ready to die. Are you?" {n}Darven spits on the ground.{/n} "You won't defeat me so easily. Mercenaries, into formation! Time to work for your gold!"

"I am ready to die. Are you?" {n}Darven spits on the ground.{/n}"We had a deal, didn't we, {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen}? Well, I'll teach you a lesson about keeping promises. {g|Mammon}Mammon{/g}! I call upon you!"
